# Welcom to My Projeckt

This is a simpel aplication writen in Python. It alows you to manage your to-do list very esily and effectivly.

## Featurs

- Add new tasks to you'r list
- Delette tasks when there done
- View all your curent task
- Save and lod your tasks from disk

## Instalation

To install the aplication, you must have Python 3 instaled.

```bash
pip instal todo-ap
